<h2>You've been invited to Court Report!</h2>

<p><strong><%= @inviter.name %></strong> wants you to set up <strong><%= @team_name %></strong> on Court Report — the tennis team management app.</p>

<% if @message.present? %>
  <p style="background:#f7f9fc;padding:16px;border-radius:8px;border-left:3px solid #c9a84c;margin:20px 0;font-style:italic;">"<%= @message %>"</p>
<% end %>

<p>As captain, you can:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Enter the season schedule</li>
  <li>Share a join link with the team</li>
  <li>Track availability and set lineups</li>
  <li>Enter match scores</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top:20px;">
  <a href="https://yourcourtreport.com/signup" style="display:inline-block;padding:12px 24px;background:#c9a84c;color:#060f1e;font-weight:bold;text-decoration:none;border-radius:8px;">Get Started</a>
</p>

<p style="margin-top:20px;color:#666;font-size:0.85em;">Court Report — Track your teams, lineups, and availability</p>
